{"tid":1851412,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一圖話你知點解要比醫護人員優先買mask","createTime":"2020-01-30T04:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T04:49:43.000Z","uid":219742,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9fae729a44ab378efaf36301a1746fd679fe6f9f","tid":1851412,"uid":219742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:31:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為E家醫管局提供既mask 係防唔到武漢肺炎既！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XNfhKBt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXNfhKBt.jpg&h=95db0a41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWHO 指出建議醫護人員最少要用ASTM 2 既mask <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TErs6QB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTErs6QB.jpg&h=0f769ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而醫管局上年因不知明原因，將大部分surgical mask 由ASTM LV 2 變左做 Astm lv 1 。 更聲稱佢地買既 lv 1 mask 比lv 3 更加好。 而市面上幾乎所有mask 都已經係lv 2 以上。<br />\n<br />\n為左前線手足健康，請大家讓醫護優先買mask <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#"},{"pid":"ec4cb879495fbb6465d512e299ee4eda26b7fdd4","tid":1851412,"uid":219742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:31:53.000Z","msg":"自推1連"},{"pid":"fa4712b15abfbac77128e01e105b26dc5a964a92","tid":1851412,"uid":219742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:34:02.000Z","msg":"自推2連"},{"pid":"5d572a42838c299840d313b8b5cfd9c5e52d1a27","tid":1851412,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:34:45.000Z","msg":"level 1<br />\n屌佢老母"},{"pid":"9c3a98eab4e12168f7cb03ed8cb8a6b3aa6053fd","tid":1851412,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:35:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedd225a9202d9d9b297f05f8a8a690402fced3e","tid":185141